Description:
    Creates a new basic front-end web application for banners.

Options:
    

Example:
    yo banner

    This will create:
        Gruntfile.js: Configuration for the task runner.
        bower.json: Front-end packages installed by bower.
        package.json: Development packages installed by npm.

        app/: Your application files.



Grunt commands:

grunt serve --target=[WIDTH]x[HEIGHT]
grunt build --target=[WIDTH]x[HEIGHT]
grunt sprite


Sub Generator:

yo banner:add [WIDTH]x[HEIGHT]